        <title type="html"><![CDATA[计算机网络 第三章 数据链路层]]></title>
        <id>https://songdlut.github.io/post/ji-suan-ji-wang-luo-di-san-zhang-shu-ju-lian-lu-ceng/</id>
        <link href="https://songdlut.github.io/post/ji-suan-ji-wang-luo-di-san-zhang-shu-ju-lian-lu-ceng/">
        </link>
        <updated>2020-10-09T13:08:39.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-数据链路层功能">1 数据链路层功能</h2>
<h2 id="成帧">成帧</h2>
<h2 id="差错控制">差错控制</h2>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/0ySkIx.png" alt="0ySkIx.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h2 id="流量控制">流量控制</h2>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/0yZuVO.png" alt="0yZuVO.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>窗口大小都是固定的</strong></p>
<h3 id="单帧滑动窗口与停止等待协议">单帧滑动窗口与停止等待协议</h3>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/0yaSL8.png" alt="0yaSL8.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3 id="多帧滑动窗口与后退n帧协议gbn">多帧滑动窗口与后退N帧协议(GBN)</h3>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06PWSP.png" alt="06PWSP.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06iKkd.png" alt="06iKkd.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06Fy8I.png" alt="06Fy8I.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06kuRI.png" alt="06kuRI.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06AD1I.png" alt="06AD1I.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06A53n.png" alt="06A53n.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06AON4.png" alt="06AON4.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h3 id="多帧滑动窗口与选择重传协议sr">多帧滑动窗口与选择重传协议(SR)</h3>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06VZoF.png" alt="06VZoF.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06eJ8H.png" alt="06eJ8H.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06eOqx.png" alt="06eOqx.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06mVdf.png" alt="06mVdf.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06nm0x.png" alt="06nm0x.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/10/06mgYD.png" alt="06mgYD.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="介质访问控制">介质访问控制</h2>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0g89S0.png" alt="0g89S0.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3 id="信道划分介质访问控制">信道划分介质访问控制</h3>
<ol>
<li>FDM</li>
<li>TDM
<ol>
<li>注意STDM,使用集中器</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>WDM</li>
<li>CDM</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="随机访问介质访问控制">随机访问介质访问控制</h3>
<h4 id="aloha协议">ALOHA协议</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gUBn0.png" alt="0gUBn0.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h4 id="csma协议carrier-sense-multiple-access载波侦听多路访问">CSMA协议(Carrier Sense Multiple Access,载波侦听多路访问)</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gakgs.png" alt="0gakgs.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ol>
<li>1-坚持CSMA<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gaJDx.png" alt="0gaJDx.png" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>非坚持CSMA<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gy4u4.png" alt="0gy4u4.png" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>p-坚持CSMA<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gyetx.png" alt="0gyetx.png" loading="lazy"><br>
缺点:冲突了还是会把数据发完,造成浪费</li>
<li>对比<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0g6C5t.png" alt="0g6C5t.png" loading="lazy"></li>
</ol>
<h4 id="csmacdcollision-detection">CSMA/CD(Collision Detection)</h4>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/11/0gcGfP.png" alt="0gcGfP.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0RUEkT.png" alt="0RUEkT.png" loading="lazy"><br>
书上的图只是为了得到2τ,CSMA/CD的根本目的为了在传输完成前就可以检测到碰撞进而停止发送,而不是让他们发送出去之后检测到碰撞<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0Rw4HI.png" alt="0Rw4HI.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0R0mUx.png" alt="0R0mUx.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0R03KH.png" alt="0R03KH.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h4 id="csmacacollision-avoidance">CSMA/CA(Collision Avoidance)</h4>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0Rs4t1.png" alt="0Rs4t1.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3 id="轮询访问介质访问控制令牌传递协议">轮询访问介质访问控制:令牌传递协议</h3>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0R2YZD.png" alt="0R2YZD.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0RWoaF.png" alt="0RWoaF.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h3 id="小结">小结</h3>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0RgUg0.png" alt="0RgUg0.png" loading="lazy"><br>
只有第二类随机访问介质访问控制会产生冲突<br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0RfCPH.png" alt="0RfCPH.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="局域网">局域网</h2>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0WlOL8.png" alt="0WlOL8.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0W1mFJ.png" alt="0W1mFJ.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0W3YuV.png" alt="0W3YuV.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0W333n.png" alt="0W333n.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0W8Svq.png" alt="0W8Svq.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0W8txI.png" alt="0W8txI.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/12/0W86Rs.png" alt="0W86Rs.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h3 id="以太网">以太网</h3>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/13/0f7qb9.png" alt="0f7qb9.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/13/0fHQbj.png" alt="0fHQbj.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/13/0fHaMF.png" alt="0fHaMF.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/13/0fHOsg.png" alt="0fHOsg.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h3 id="ieee-80211">IEEE 802.11</h3>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/13/0hpzGQ.png" alt="0hpzGQ.png" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/13/0h98IO.png" alt="0h98IO.png" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="广域网">广域网</h2>
<h3 id="ppp协议">PPP协议</h3>
